                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A shapechanged ossiworm agent can revert to its natural form as a move action. Any creature within 30 feet who can see this process becomes shaken for 1d6 rounds (Will DC 19 negates). This is an emotion, fear, mind-affecting, and sense-dependent effect.",
